Getting started is simple.

Getting started is simple.

A simple, three step process to getting your life organised.

1

Install Simplicity

Get up and running in minutes—download and install the app to start simplifying your workflow immediately.

2

Add Your Tasks

Quickly add and organize your to-dos. Stay focused on what matters most, without the clutter.

3

Track and Complete

See your progress at a glance as you tick off tasks. Stay productive and in control, one step at a time.
